Hello <%= @property.user.full_name %>,

Your service request has been completed by <%= @service.name %>! 

Completion details:
	<% if @service_request.location_verified && @service_request.timestamp_verified %>
  Verified completed by HumbleCasa
  <% end %>
	Completion date: <%= DateTime.parse(@service_request.completed_date.to_s).in_time_zone(@service_request.property.time_zone).strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %>
	Completed by: <%= @service_request.user.full_name %>
  Service charge: <%= number_to_currency(@service_request.charge) %>
  <% if !@service_request.charge_notes.blank? %>
  Charge explanation: <%= @service_request.charge_notes %>
  <% end %>
	<% if !@service_request.completion_note.empty? %>
  Notes: <%= @service_request.completion_note %>
  <% end %>
  <% if @service_request.service_photo_1? || @service_request.service_photo_2? || @service_request.service_photo_3? %>
  Service photos:
  <%= image_tag @service_request.service_photo_1_url if @service_request.service_photo_1? %>
  <%= image_tag @service_request.service_photo_2_url if @service_request.service_photo_2? %>
  <%= image_tag @service_request.service_photo_3_url if @service_request.service_photo_3? %>
  <% end %> 

Service request details:
	Request #: <%= @service_request.service_request_id %>
	Service request created on: <%= DateTime.parse(@service_request.created_at.to_s).in_time_zone(@service_request.property.time_zone).strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %>
	<% if !@service_request.instructions.empty? %>
  Special instructions for this request: <%= @service_request.instructions %>
  <% end %>
  <% if @service_request.onetime? %>
    One time request
    Service window: <%= DateTime.parse(@service_request.service_start_date.to_s).in_time_zone(@service_request.property.time_zone).strftime("%a %m/%d/%y %I:%M%p %Z") %> - <%= DateTime.parse(@service_request.service_end_date.to_s).in_time_zone(@service_request.property.time_zone).strftime("%a %m/%d/%y %I:%M%p %Z") %>
  <% else %>
    Repeating request
    Frequency: <%= @service_request.frequency.titleize.downcase %>
    <% case @service_request.frequency %>
      <% when "weekly" %> 
        on <%= @service_request.service_week_day.titleize %> of each week
      <% when "every_other_week" %>
        on <%= @service_request.service_week_day.titleize %> of every other week
      <% when "monthly" %> 
        on the <%= @service_request.service_month_day.ordinalize %> of each month
      <% when "every_other_month" %> 
        on the <%= @service_request.service_month_day.ordinalize %> of every other month
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
	
Service details:
 	<%= @service.name %>
  	Owner: <%= User.find_by_id(@service.user_id).full_name %>
  	<%= @service.phone %>
  	<%= @service.email %>


If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact your service provider.

Thank you,
The HumbleCasa Team
